The paper also mentions the use of low-density parity-check (LDPC) codes, which are commonly used in multimedia applications (cs.MM). Finally, the paper discusses the potential benefits of making channel state information (CSI) available to higher layers, which could be relevant to cybersecurity (cs.CY).
